instructions: Put the plate in center of table.
Put the Dinner Fork on the left of the plate
Put the dinner knife on the right side of the plate
Put the salad fork on the left side of the dinner fork.
Put the salad knife on the right side of the dinner fork.
Put the soup spoon on the right side of salad knife.
Put the dessert spoon above the charger with bowl pointing to left.
Put the dessert fork below the dessert spoon and have the fork prong facing right.
Put the dinner plate on top of charger.
Put the butter knife on top of bread plate.
Put the water glass above the knives.
Put the napkin on top of dinner plate.
